## Goal 4 — Better User Experience

### What It Does
Improve onboarding and usability while preserving the existing architecture. This is the least risky goal — purely frontend polish.

### Potential Improvements

| Improvement | Impact |
|---|---|
| **Guided first-run tour** (tooltips highlighting key UI elements) | Frontend only |
| **Inline help text** on each wizard step explaining *why* this data matters | Frontend only |
| **Quick-start templates** (pre-filled example semester data for demo/testing) | Frontend + one seed API |
| **Better mobile responsiveness** | Frontend CSS only |
| **Keyboard shortcuts** for common actions | Frontend only |
| **Progress indicator** showing "how much setup is left" | Frontend only |

### Risks
- Minimal. UX polish is low-risk by nature.

### Dependencies
- None. Can be done in parallel with any other goal.

