## Proposed Milestone Breakdown

> [!NOTE]
> Milestones are ordered by dependency. Each milestone is independently shippable — the app works correctly after each one.

| Milestone | Scope | Engine Impact | DB Migration |
|---|---|---|---|
| **M1 — Attendance Distribution** | Modify `slot_selector.py` to distribute skips evenly instead of deferring. Update ADD and ENGINE_ARCHITECTURE.md. Full regression testing. | ✅ Yes (`slot_selector.py` only) | ❌ No |
| **M2 — Slot Type System** | New `slot_type` table, `timetable_slot.slot_type_id` column, per-slot-type requirement calculation, updated wizard UI with type dropdown. | ✅ Yes (`requirement_calc.py`, `slot_selector.py`, `types.py`, `explanation_generator.py`) | ✅ Yes |
| **M3 — PDF Timetable Import** | PDF upload endpoint, `pdfplumber`-based table extraction, review/correction screen, confirm-and-save flow. | ❌ No | ⚠️ Maybe (temp `import_session`) |
| **M4 — Image Timetable Import (OCR)** | Image upload endpoint, Tesseract OCR extraction, same review/correction screen as M3. | ❌ No | ❌ No (reuses M3 infra) |
| **M5 — Academic Calendar Import** | PDF/image upload for academic calendars, date/event extraction, mapped to `SemesterEvent` table, review screen. | ❌ No | ❌ No |
| **M6 — UX Polish & Onboarding** | Guided tour, inline help, mobile polish, keyboard shortcuts. | ❌ No | ❌ No |
| **M7 — Documentation & Release** | SRD v1.1, TRD v1.1, ADD v1.1 updates. README screenshots. Release notes. | ❌ No | ❌ No |

